title: About Sealed Saint Graphs
message:
The Saint Graphs for "Ashiya Douman" at Stage 3 and further Ascension are sealed.

Enhance the Servant to Spirit Origin Ascension Stage 3 and clear the "Saint Graph Unlocking Quest" available within Interludes to unlock them.

title: About Sealed Saint Graphs
message:
Sen-no-Rikyu's Saint Graph from Stage 3 Ascension and higher is locked.
By completing "GUDAGUDA New Yamataikoku" & reaching Stage 3 Ascension, a "Spirit Origin Release Quest" will be unlocked in Interludes, and the Saint Graph will be unlocked upon its completion.

title: About Sealed Saint Graphs
message:
The Saint Graphs for "Charlemagne" at Stage 3 and further Ascension are sealed.

Enhance the Servant to Stage 3 Ascension and clear the "Spirit Origin Release Quest" available in Interludes to unlock them.

title: About Sealed Saint Graphs
message:
Oberon's Saint Graph from Stage 3 Ascension and higher is locked.
By completing "Fae Round Table Domain Avalon le Fae" & reaching Stage 3 Ascension, a "Spirit Origin Release Quest" will be unlocked in Interludes, and the Saint Graph will be unlocked upon its completion.
